Commentary Text: Boult to Saha, out Caught by Samson!! Saha goes for a duck. Boult deadly with the new-ball in the powerplay. The attempted inswinger on middle and off, Saha tries to whip that across the line, highly ambitious shot and nicks behind. Clear edge and he starts going as soon as Samson takes it. That's the start GT did not want as Saha was very good in the powerplay. Saha c Samson b Boult 0(2)
